title: Leg Medium Light Skin Tone
description: Depicts a leg, often used to represent movement, walking, or physical action. The medium-light skin tone specifies the individual. Can also refer to prosthetics.
apple_vendor_description: The leg emoji with a medium-light skin tone on Apple devices is rendered with Apple's signature realistic lighting and soft, rounded form, giving it a smooth and lifelike appearance. The subtle shading and gentle curve of the calf suggest natural movement and presence, making it feel tangible. This emoji on Apple devices is commonly used to indicate walking, running, or simply being present and active in a situation.
